{"id":209595,"type":2,"name":"無限戦記ポトリス","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/af/7d/209595_FQwWx.jpg","rating":{"total":3,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":2,"5":0,"6":1,"7":0,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":4.7},"summary":"《坦克王》（日文：無限戦記ポトリス；韩文：포트리스；英文：Tank Knights Fortress）为韩国网络游戏疯狂坦克改编的动画。本作是一部由2003年4月至2004年3月间，开始在日本播放的动画。台湾东森幼幼台在2006年播放，之后在2009年MOMO亲子台亦有重播、曾在中华电信MOD上档过。主要内容描述波特里斯骑士与异种人合作，并且对抗达克城的首领，以换取正义、自由与和平的故事。\r\n\r\n坦克王的故事内容是叙述一场正义与邪恶的对抗，被邪恶统治的“波特里斯”星球，统治者为了自己的野心，强迫市民建造“巴别塔”，并使居民活在水深火热当中。正义波特里斯骑士的出现，与邪恶力量的对抗战役正式展开。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>坦克王</li><li><span>话数: </span>52</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>2003年4月5日</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/2624\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">鴫野彰</a></li><li><span>分镜: </span><a href=\"/person/28408\">さくら十四郎</a></li><li><span>音乐: </span><a href=\"/person/1849\">福島祐子</a>、<a href=\"/person/20763\">椎名KAY太</a></li><li><span>人物设定: </span><a href=\"/person/1060\">高谷浩利</a></li><li><span>系列构成: </span><a href=\"/person/218\">藤田伸三</a></li><li><span>制片人: </span><a href=\"/person/3111\">笹田直樹</a></li><li><span>动画制作: </span><a href=\"/person/189\">サンライズ</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>疯狂坦克</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>포트리스</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Mugen Senki Portriss</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Tank Knights Fortress</li><li><span>播放电视台: </span>东京电视台</li><li><span>播放结束: </span>2004年3月27日</li>","collection":{"wish":5,"collect":6,"on_hold":1,"dropped":2},"eps":[{"id":700162,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/700162","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":700163,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/700163","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":700164,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/700164","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":700165,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/700165","type":0,"sort":4,"